---
title: Farmer's Market Egg and Salmon Sandwich with Blueberry and Tangerine Salad
description: Eggs are perfect for dinner! Quick to make and goes with everything, this sandwich is so fresh but luxurious, paired with smoked salmon and avocado with a fresh fruity salad!
